  "script": [
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "对话一：怪老师的私信升级 (Guai Laoshi's DMs Escalate)",
      "en": "Dialogue 1: 怪老师's DMs escalate."
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "女生群聊",
      "en": "Girls' group chat."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "怪老师又发私信了。越来越过分。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "[截图]"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "太恶心了。他在评论我的衣服。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "[截图]"
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "text": "> 怪老师：清清，你的作文写得太好了。你是我教过的最有才华的学生。你有没有想过读研？我可以给你写推荐信。",
      "en": "> 怪老师: 清清, your essay is so well-written. You're the most talented student I've ever taught. Have you thought about grad school? I could write you a recommendation letter."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "太假了。用学术的名义。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "小李呢？他给你发什么了？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "也发了。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "说什么？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "说他的办公室随时open。如果我想聊天可以去找他。他泡了茶。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "\"泡了茶\"？？！太过分了！"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "……但其实挺sweet的？他注意到我最近不太开心。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "小李。老师不应该给你发这种私信。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "注意：他只给女生发。王崩和矮中没收到。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "……也许是因为我们需要更多帮助？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "他有病。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "你们想太多了。"
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "对话二：Shopping——女生出去逛街 (Girls Go Shopping)",
      "en": "Dialogue 2: Shopping -- Girls go out."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "我需要买新衣服。什么颜色好看？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "你喜欢什么颜色就买什么颜色。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "我想要显白的颜色。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "别给我那个表情。黑色和深蓝色显白。这是common sense。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "你穿什么都好看。别overthink。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "太白了。显得我更黑。",
      "sub": "拿起一件白色上衣，在镜子前比了比，放下了"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "小黑。你的皮肤没有问题。是标准有问题。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你知道一白遮三丑吗？这不是我发明的。这是中国文化说的。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "中国文化说了很多东西。不是每一个都对。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "这个多少钱？",
      "sub": "试了一件oversize的黑色卫衣"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "narrator",
      "zh": "二百八。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "有没有更大的size？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "narrator",
      "zh": "那个已经是最大号了。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "那就这个吧。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你买的衣服都像你爸爸的。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaoli",
      "zh": "舒服就行。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "这个呢？",
      "sub": "试了一件结构感很强的blazer"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "太正式了吧。你去上班还是去上课？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……我平时就是这样穿的。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "那就是问题所在。来。穿这个。"
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "text": "她递给清清一件简单的黑色T恤。清清看了一下。穿上了。看了看镜子。",
      "en": "She hands 清清 a simple black T-shirt. 清清 looks at it. Puts it on. Checks the mirror."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "卧槽。清清。你……"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……什么？"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你好看。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "请停下来。"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "我说真的。矮中看到你这样穿会——"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "我不是为矮中穿的！"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "那你为什么脸红了？"
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "Ch 11: 了 (completed action)",
